casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Kristan L. PETERS-HAMLIN.
No. D-2897.
Supreme Court of the United States
May 16, 2016.
Kristan L. Peters-Hamlin, of Westport, Connecticut, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why she should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
